<strong>IN&#45;TEXT CITATION</strong>
<br><br>
Put a footnote number in your text to show when you are using another person&#8217;s ideas or words.
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	&hellip;has been recently identified.<sup>1</sup>
</blockquote>
<br>
This number directs your reader to a footnote at the bottom of your page. The footnote contains information about the work you are citing, including details of the work, and relevant page number(s).
<br><br>
<strong>FOOTNOTES</strong>
<br><br>
Footnotes are placed in numerical order at the bottom of the page. In the case of most assignment papers and essays where footnotes and a bibliography are used, the footnote citation details can be quite brief (Example B) because the full details are found in the bibliography. However, if you are instructed by your tutor or lecturer to provide a full reference in the footnote the first time a work is cited, see Example A. If the work is cited again, use the short form (Example B).  When the author is anonymous, begin the footnote 
with the title of the work.
<br><br>
When shortened references to the same work follow each other with no other references in&#45;between, replace the title and publication details with <strong>ibid</strong>. (Example C) and the page number if it differs from the previous citation (Example D).
<br><br>
<strong>Example A</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">1. &#34;Study Smarter, Not Harder: Setting Goals to Improve Your Academic Performance,&#34; <em>Student Review</em> 25, no. 5 (2056): 12.</span>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example B</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">7. &#34;Study Smarter, Not Harder,&#34; 11.</span>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example C</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">8. Ibid.</span>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example D</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">9. Ibid., 25&#45;6.</span>
</blockquote>
